    section
      .wrapper
        h2 What is Z-router ?
        p Z-router is a light javascript router based on the hash <span class="inline-code">#</span> part of the url allowing you to display inline or ajax-fetched templates.
        p No dependencies are required, It is very simple to use and is very flexible with the possibility to add options to each route and get parameters from the url.

        .grid
          .grid-2.center
            .box
              a(href="http://github.com/benavern/z-router", data-ztooltips="View this project on Github").btn.z-tooltips-top
                span.entypo-github
                | &nbsp; github

          .grid-2.center
            .box
              a(href="download", data-ztooltips="Download the js script").btn
                span.entypo-download
                | &nbsp; download

